build.help_snippet:
Usage: reversan [MODE] [OPTIONS]

Modes:
--help, -h                                Display this help message.
--play                                    Play against the engine in terminal interface.
--bot-vs-bot                              Start game where the engine plays against itself.
--benchmark                               Run search on pre-defined state.

Additional Options:
--depth, -d <1 - 49> [10]                           Set the engine's search depth.
--engine, -e <negascout | alphabeta> [negascout]    Choose the tree search algorithm.
--threads, -t, <1 - 8> [1]                          EXPERIMENTAL, negascout only.
--disable-tp                                        Disables transposition tables.
--order, -o <line_by_line | opt1 | opt2> [opt1]     Sets search order of the engine.
--style, -s <basic | solarized | dracula> [basic]   Specify UI style.
